      <p class="hero-sub">We embed inside your business — driving real innovation, building new revenue streams, and making AI work for you. Not theory. Results.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start a conversation <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        <a href="#work" class="btn btn-ghost-dark">See our work</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="hero-side">
      <div class="hero-side-label">
        <span>// Live Index</span>
        <span>2026.Q2</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hs-row"><div class="num">12+</div><div class="lbl">Years embedded with clients</div></div>
      <div class="hs-row"><div class="num">40+</div><div class="lbl">Products shipped across industries</div></div>
      <div class="hs-row"><div class="num">100%</div><div class="lbl">Year-one client retention</div></div>
      <div class="hs-row"><div class="num">£28M</div><div class="lbl">New revenue unlocked for partners</div></div>
      <div class="hs-foot"><span>Methodology</span><span class="arrow">→</span></div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TRUST STRIP -->
<div class="trust on-dark">
  <div class="trust-inner">
    <div class="trust-left">
      <div class="label">// Selected Partners</div>
      <div class="copy">40+ brands &amp; partner agencies have trusted us with their hardest problems.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-right">
      <div class="logo-track" id="logo-track"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- CLIENT VOICES -->
<section class="voices on-dark">
  <div class="voices-inner">
    <div class="voices-head">
      <div>
        <div class="label"><span class="num">// </span>Client voices</div>
        <p class="lead">Don't take our word for it — here's what it's like to have us embedded in the room.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="voices-nav">
        <button id="voices-prev" aria-label="Previous reviews"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M15 18l-6-6 6-6"/></svg></button>
        <button id="voices-next" aria-label="More reviews"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg></button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="voices-track" id="voices-track">
      <div class="voice">
        <div class="voice-mark">"</div>
        <p class="voice-text">They didn't behave like an agency. They behaved like <em>part of our team</em> — and shipped things our internal crew had been stuck on for a year.</p>
        <div class="voice-attr">
          <div class="voice-name">Annabel Karmel</div>
          <div class="voice-role">Founder <span class="co">// Annabel Karmel</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="voice">
        <div class="voice-mark">"</div>
        <p class="voice-text">We went from paper forms to <em>real-time visibility</em> across hundreds of field engineers. Adoption was the part I worried about — it turned out to be the easy part.</p>
        <div class="voice-attr">
          <div class="voice-name">Operations Director</div>
          <div class="voice-role">Field Services <span class="co">// Pocket Inspector</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="voice">
        <div class="voice-mark">"</div>
        <p class="voice-text">Practical, fast, and refreshingly free of jargon. They cut through the AI hype and built something that <em>actually moved our numbers</em>.</p>
        <div class="voice-attr">
          <div class="voice-name">Head of Product</div>
          <div class="voice-role">Risk Platform <span class="co">// ProvaRISK</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="voice">
        <div class="voice-mark">"</div>
        <p class="voice-text">They asked the questions our own team had stopped asking. The result was a product that finally <em>felt like us</em> — only sharper.</p>
        <div class="voice-attr">
          <div class="voice-name">Managing Director</div>
          <div class="voice-role">Wellness Platform <span class="co">// Wellspace</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="voice">
        <div class="voice-mark">"</div>
        <p class="voice-text">Most partners disappear after launch. This lot <em>stayed embedded</em>, kept measuring, and kept pushing the numbers in the right direction.</p>
        <div class="voice-attr">
          <div class="voice-name">Founder</div>
          <div class="voice-role">Venue Tech <span class="co">// Value for Venues</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="voice">
        <div class="voice-mark">"</div>
        <p class="voice-text">Calm, capable, and honest about trade-offs. We trusted them with our hardest problem and they <em>didn't flinch</em>.</p>
        <div class="voice-attr">
          <div class="voice-name">CTO</div>
          <div class="voice-role">Security <span class="co">// Locus Security</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICES -->
<section class="section services" id="services">
  <div class="services-inner">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow"><span class="bar"></span><span class="num">01</span><span>What we do</span></div>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top:20px;">Built to move<br />fast. Built to last.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="section-sub">Four areas, one mission: give your organisation an unfair advantage through smart technology and fearless thinking — without the consultant theatre.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-num">// 01 — STRATEGY</div>
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 2v4M12 18v4M2 12h4M18 12h4M5 5l3 3M16 16l3 3M5 19l3-3M16 8l3-3"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-title">AI Strategy</h3>
        <p class="service-desc">We cut through the hype and build a practical AI roadmap that aligns with your goals — identifying where automation and intelligence can create the biggest impact.</p>
        <div class="service-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M7 17L17 7M7 7h10v10"/></svg></div>
      </article>
      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-num">// 02 — BUILD</div>
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M3 6h18M3 12h18M3 18h18M8 3v18M16 3v18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-title">Product Development</h3>
        <p class="service-desc">From early concept to launch-ready product, we design and build digital products that are intuitive, scalable, and deeply rooted in user needs.</p>
        <div class="service-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M7 17L17 7M7 7h10v10"/></svg></div>
      </article>
      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-num">// 03 — INNOVATE</div>
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M8 3l4 8 4-8M3 12h18M8 21l4-8 4 8"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-title">Development Innovation</h3>
        <p class="service-desc">We don't just build to spec — we challenge assumptions and introduce modern engineering practices that future-proof what you're building today.</p>
        <div class="service-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M7 17L17 7M7 7h10v10"/></svg></div>
      </article>
      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-num">// 04 — AUTOMATE</div>
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-3-6.7"/><path d="M21 4v5h-5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="service-title">Process Automation</h3>
        <p class="service-desc">Manual processes slow teams down and introduce risk. We identify, design, and implement automations that free your people up to focus on what matters.</p>
        <div class="service-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M7 17L17 7M7 7h10v10"/></svg></div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="services-cta">
      <div class="services-cta-inner">
        <p><strong>We don't do cookie-cutter.</strong> Every engagement starts with understanding your business from the inside out — then we design solutions that fit.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Talk to us <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WORK -->
<section class="section work" id="work">
  <div class="work-inner">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow"><span class="bar"></span><span class="num">02</span><span>Selected work</span></div>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top:20px;">Real results,<br />real partners.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="section-sub">We go beyond the brief — embedding with our clients to drive outcomes that actually move the needle.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cs-featured" id="cs-featured"></div>

    <div class="cs-controls">
      <div class="cs-dots" id="cs-dots"></div>
      <div class="cs-nav">
        <button id="cs-prev" aria-label="Previous case study"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M15 18l-6-6 6-6"/></svg></button>
        <button id="cs-next" aria-label="Next case study"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- AI -->
<section class="section ai-section">
  <div class="ai-inner">
    <div class="ai-content">
      <div class="eyebrow on-dark"><span class="bar"></span><span class="num">03</span><span>AI &amp; Innovation</span></div>
