      <p class="section-sub on-dark" style="margin-top:24px; max-width:520px;">Most businesses are overwhelmed by the pace of AI change. We help you cut through the noise — identifying real opportunities, building practical solutions, and embedding intelligence into the work you already do.</p>
      <div style="margin-top:32px;">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Explore what's possible <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ai-grid">
      <div class="ai-card">
        <div class="ai-num">// UNDERSTAND</div>
        <div class="ai-card-title">AI Readiness Audit</div>
        <p class="ai-card-desc">We assess where your business is today and map the highest-value AI opportunities.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ai-card">
        <div class="ai-num">// BUILD</div>
        <div class="ai-card-title">Custom AI Solutions</div>
        <p class="ai-card-desc">Not off-the-shelf. We design and build AI tools that fit your exact workflows.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ai-card">
        <div class="ai-num">// AUTOMATE</div>
        <div class="ai-card-title">Intelligent Automation</div>
        <p class="ai-card-desc">Replace manual, repetitive tasks with smart automations that scale with you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ai-card">
        <div class="ai-num">// GROW</div>
        <div class="ai-card-title">Revenue Innovation</div>
        <p class="ai-card-desc">Identify and build entirely new revenue streams powered by technology and data.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROCESS -->
<section class="section process" id="process">
  <div class="process-inner">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow"><span class="bar"></span><span class="num">04</span><span>How we work</span></div>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top:20px;">Embedded.<br />Honest. Fast.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="section-sub">We're not a vendor — we're an extension of your team. Four steps, no theatre, real momentum from week one.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-num-line"></div>
        <div class="process-num">// STEP 01</div>
        <h3 class="process-title">Discovery</h3>
        <p class="process-desc">We get under the skin of your business — your goals, blockers, and the biggest opportunities hiding in plain sight.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-num-line"></div>
        <div class="process-num">// STEP 02</div>
        <h3 class="process-title">Strategy</h3>
        <p class="process-desc">A practical, prioritised plan — not a 60-page deck. Clear, actionable, built around your actual constraints.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-num-line"></div>
        <div class="process-num">// STEP 03</div>
        <h3 class="process-title">Build</h3>
        <p class="process-desc">We move fast without cutting corners. Iterative delivery, constant feedback, real users involved from day one.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-num-line"></div>
        <div class="process-num">// STEP 04</div>
        <h3 class="process-title">Scale</h3>
        <p class="process-desc">We don't disappear after launch. We stay embedded, measuring impact and continuing to drive growth.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="section about" id="about">
