        <p class="afc-quote">"We were tired of watching great businesses get handed slide decks instead of <em>real change</em>. So we built the partner we always wished we'd had — one that rolls up its sleeves, sits inside your team, and stays until the work actually ships."</p>
        <div class="afc-sign">
          <span class="afc-names">[Founder Name] &amp; [Founder Name]</span>
          <span class="afc-roles">// Co-founders, Applikation</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="bar"></span><span class="num">05</span><span>About us</span></div>
