        </div>
        <div class="about-value">
          <div class="av-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M5 12l4-9 6 9-3 9-7-9z"/><path d="M9 3l3 9"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <div class="av-title">Forefront of what's next</div>
            <p class="av-desc">We stay ahead so you don't have to — bringing emerging technology and fresh thinking when it matters most.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INSIGHTS -->
<section class="section insights">
  <div class="insights-inner">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow"><span class="bar"></span><span class="num">06</span><span>Insights</span></div>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top:20px;">Thinking out loud.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="section-sub">Field notes from the work — practical takes on AI, product, and the messy reality of building things that ship.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="insights-grid">
