      <p class="section-sub on-dark" style="margin-top:20px;">No sales pitch. Just an honest conversation about where you want to go and how we might help you get there faster.</p>
      <div class="contact-detail-list" style="margin-top:40px;">
        <div class="contact-detail">
          <div class="cd-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="14" rx="0"/><path d="M3 7l9 6 9-6"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <div class="cd-label">// Email</div>
            <div class="cd-value">hello@applikation.co.uk</div>
